{"tid":339263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林一鳴：樓市已見頂 供應增勢加速跌勢","createTime":"2017-07-29T02:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T05:08:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"044602cc952fbfbca199a583531a241d15c68e6c","tid":339263,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170728/large/1501215306_61f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170728%2Flarge%2F1501215306_61f7.jpg&h=5b2adf1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n運房局公佈上一季數字顯示，未來3至4年私樓供應達9.8萬伙，創下新高位，資深分析員林一鳴認為，樓市已於6至7月見頂，加上未來新供應陸續到位，會加速樓市跌勢，跌勢將會分兩個階段，今年底前樓價會有向下5%至10%壓力，當樓價回調5%至10%幅度後，會吸引部份買家入市，甚或令樓市出現假小陽春，其後，明年供應陸續增多，息口趨升等因素催化下，明年出璋第二階段跌勢。他預期，各類物業市場中，中小型住宅過去有「炒過籠」情況，細戶樓價下調壓力將較大。"},{"pid":"2f5b20416ddd8d83d3bfc357d74477250ec4cbb1","tid":339263,"uid":40763,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:11:47.000Z","msg":"專家？叫佢食屎啦"},{"pid":"d686c0187e4e650d8cc0627c3c5e92bd2b74ba8b","tid":339263,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:15:32.000Z","msg":"跌啦跌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 炒樓炒得咁撚開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098abd291af65f5bc68449b4f2bc778aa84c65ad","tid":339263,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:16:41.000Z","msg":"董建華時期既瘋狂供應都未去到呢個LEVEL"},{"pid":"b42b8dde6bc20d3b48be9a1f657fd451fa3f621e","tid":339263,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跌啦跌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 炒樓炒得咁撚開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有SSD 之後仲點有得抄呀？<br />\n<br />\n連登仔真係乜都唔識思想仲停係上世紀"},{"pid":"0ecb7b4543ed32c7216b8bd333aff11bf72a1a97","tid":339263,"uid":59575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跌啦跌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 炒樓炒得咁撚開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有SSD 之後仲點有得抄呀？<br />\n<br />\n連登仔真係乜都唔識思想仲停係上世紀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nssd 只不過儲貨長左兩三年..點會無得炒 e家17年咪沽番14年d 貨...好簡單<br />\n覺得無得炒係你本少"},{"pid":"8bf38c9c5537eb2e1dc4ea98f43bb2f457e57e81","tid":339263,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:24:05.000Z","msg":"其實香港從來都唔係「無屋住」<br />\n而係「買唔起樓」<br />\n<br />\n其實唔少人都係租屋住, 絕大部份人都係有屋住<br />\n買唔起咪租囉<br />\n唔明有乜問題"},{"pid":"3d3c3803c02294bca801eb936e1f7a2faacbec39","tid":339263,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:24:25.000Z","msg":"佢年年吹跌<br />\n上次加息又吹跌。<br />\n最後升返<br />\n根本香港剛需好強<br />\n強到個個做奴隸"},{"pid":"f7f074875e41cb8206470640670abe3ee6f048a6","tid":339263,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>董建華時期既瘋狂供應都未去到呢個LEVEL</blockquote><br />\n唔係喎，董建華好似多少少，佢有一兩年係成50000個per year(好似係)，而家係30000個per year(加埋公屋就4萬)，不過如果真係持續3年做到4萬per year都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAnyway,其實都同董建華差不多架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好期待支那入左市個d輸到pk"},{"pid":"eb4360be41f243dc6e7e3cf9bbd5e13fe16b44e6","tid":339263,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:38:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實香港從來都唔係「無屋住」<br />\n而係「買唔起樓」<br />\n<br />\n其實唔少人都係租屋住, 絕大部份人都係有屋住<br />\n買唔起咪租囉<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔明有乜問題</span></blockquote><br />\nTrue<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68f857dc7e0a2bac8559bc85042b120ae652f3d","tid":339263,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"643cd7d34b9d67539b7daa01d25045d415673092","tid":339263,"uid":116443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實香港從來都唔係「無屋住」<br />\n而係「買唔起樓」<br />\n<br />\n其實唔少人都係租屋住, 絕大部份人都係有屋住<br />\n買唔起咪租囉<br />\n唔明有乜問題</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你知唔知租有幾貴<br />\n一個唔係俾人住嗰地方最少5k，住得人嘅地方起碼倍大兩至三倍價錢<br />\n到你結埋婚有仔有女仲租屋住？都on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5784b6b944ccb2f02141d8070473e5db0bd1e41","tid":339263,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>董建華時期既瘋狂供應都未去到呢個LEVEL</blockquote><br />\n老董時期十二萬一年都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家三四年加埋先八九萬</blockquote><br />\n如果30000個per year係追返上港英時代個supply<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過都好多了，如果除開4年，20000個per year就少d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e37fd32eb1e945d4461109e283496881260672d","tid":339263,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:45:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>董建華時期既瘋狂供應都未去到呢個LEVEL</blockquote><br />\n老董時期十二萬一年都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家三四年加埋先八九萬</blockquote><br />\n如果30000個per year係追返上港英時代個supply<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過都好多了，如果除開4年，20000個per year就少d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十二萬一年係邊年？我記得最勁好似70000一年(加公屋)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108c1553f42f6efc953989245381ce93a6fcc566","tid":339263,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:54:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6646743389b43e5f4963f67ba0974085e86d3f51","tid":339263,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實香港從來都唔係「無屋住」<br />\n而係「買唔起樓」<br />\n<br />\n其實唔少人都係租屋住, 絕大部份人都係有屋住<br />\n買唔起咪租囉<br />\n唔明有乜問題</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你知唔知租有幾貴<br />\n一個唔係俾人住嗰地方最少5k，住得人嘅地方起碼倍大兩至三倍價錢<br />\n到你結埋婚有仔有女仲租屋住？都on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜你依家供樓可以低過 5K?<br />\n供樓好平？ <br />\nON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n供樓唔駛出首期?<br />\n租樓唔駛出首期喎！<br />\n<br />\n坦白講, 事實真相就係, 本來無首期, 只應租樓既人, 想買樓<br />\n但樓價太高, 無首期, 然後話「無屋住」 <br />\n(其實佢自己係住緊, 唔係訓街, 只係租屋住)"},{"pid":"520f4dc3fa802e20ccbbcaf6d9901e6a599e9a48","tid":339263,"uid":77256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"話佢跌 其實跟本就唔會跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係跌個時 你唔會估到<br />\n<br />\n而且跌個時你都唔會買得到 或者跟本唔會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a29bbd1ea70201439b989661df50cc53d3003f","tid":339263,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>董建華時期既瘋狂供應都未去到呢個LEVEL</blockquote><br />\n係3-4年10萬呀傻仔<br />\n<br />\n一年得兩萬，好多？"},{"pid":"6f13767fa8c1cc75698c15918f02feba882222fe","tid":339263,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>董建華時期既瘋狂供應都未去到呢個LEVEL</blockquote><br />\n老董時期十二萬一年都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家三四年加埋先八九萬</blockquote><br />\n如果30000個per year係追返上港英時代個supply<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過都好多了，如果除開4年，20000個per year就少d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十二萬一年係邊年？我記得最勁好似70000一年(加公屋)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係2001年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2001年十萬係加晒公屋、居屋、私樓全撚部呀<br />\n<br />\nON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f73fbda09d525286c9f3e9484af1f897f6abc7","tid":339263,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>董建華時期既瘋狂供應都未去到呢個LEVEL</blockquote><br />\n係3-4年10萬呀傻仔<br />\n<br />\n一年得兩萬，好多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一年2.5萬私樓唔多?<br />\n<br />\n世界上邊個大型城市係一年起到2.5萬私樓? 你講黎聽下！"},{"pid":"568565958d8a0ba8115ea658e2ebcf373724d090","tid":339263,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:05:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7240439090bc5776f584960e0330fb98eaf4b713","tid":339263,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:10:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34f31753cc883862f59d7840efa9beac3d64d5b0","tid":339263,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"除非經濟差到銀行都唔借錢，減左一班full pay唔到既人，有錢full pay既咪無機會囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，就咁增加供應大把人借盡都接啦如果平2-3成"},{"pid":"b2cfc60202d940e4da2970b4abe8c57317bbdcd7","tid":339263,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:22:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>董建華時期既瘋狂供應都未去到呢個LEVEL</blockquote><br />\n唔係喎，董建華好似多少少，佢有一兩年係成50000個per year(好似係)，而家係30000個per year(加埋公屋就4萬)，不過如果真係持續3年做到4萬per year都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAnyway,其實都同董建華差不多架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好期待支那入左市個d輸到pk</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n董建華個個年代有幾多大陸人買樓？"},{"pid":"7b357d66e027729112934d98a360dcc444fe246d","tid":339263,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:25:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}